metadata.name: A Jumping Jack
metadata.description:
Have you ever wondered if we are really alive?
Or do we have to wear a mask every day and be controlled by other people?
Meanwhile, women are indirectly under domination even in the form of freedom. What body is better, what clothes are sexier, what makeup is fashionable, even how to behave is more desirable, how to have sex is more attractive and...
But are these things really what she wants? Didn't she turn into a walking dead before that time when she wanted something?
